5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

<undefined-text-style-mapping>

Sealed instantiable class

Summary

The class of undefined text style mappings.

Superclasses

<error>

Init-keywords

port:
An instance of type <port>. Required.

text-style:
An instance of type <text-style>. Required.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

The class of undefined text style mappings. This class is used for any text styles that have not had mappings defined for a given port.

Operations

None.
